{
  "chapter": 63,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十八章\"情锁秦宫\"。项少龙在乌府接待图先谋士肖月潭，获赠四副用珍稀豹麟兽皮特制的易容面具，供往赵国行事之用。肖月潭透露前日伏击乃渭南武士行馆所为，吕不韦另有铲除阳泉君、邱日升的计划，请项少龙暂且忍耐。随后朱姬召项少龙入宫，在御花园中先是表达感激与栽培政儿之心，又旧情流露，感叹未能在邯郸将身体托付。最后道出真正目的：请项少龙赴赵时杀死曾凌辱她的乐乘。她先以赵雅试探项少龙反应，再说明真相，用眼泪和誓言打动项少龙。二人在君臣之礼与旧日情愫间游走，终以项少龙承诺杀乐乘、朱姬许诺引介寡妇清作别。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是相国着鄙人来找太傅，看看有什么可帮得上忙的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "先生请勿见外，叫在下少龙便成，无论我官至何职，我们既是曾共患难的朋友，只以平辈论交。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为方便少龙往赵国行事，纯靠易容化装，既麻烦又不妥当，所以相国命肖某特别为少龙、小俊、滕兄和乌兄四位，依脸型特制了四块精巧的面具，只要略加化装，例如修改鬓发形状和色泽，保证可瞒过赵穆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然！少龙等要在声音和举止方面多加配合，否则仍会给辨认出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "相国想得真周到，不知东西带来了没有。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "设计最巧妙的地方，是接口多在毛发处，例如露出眼睛的眼形缺口，不但把你的眉毛加浓，还把眼型变圆，所以即使熟识你的人，亦不能由眼睛把你辨认出来，至于颚下的接口，涂上一层粉油，便天衣无缝。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这面具仍要做少许修补，三天内即可交货。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "肖先生真是神乎其技，只凭记忆竟可制造出这么恰到好处的面具，这究竟用的是什么材料？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是产于西北一种叫'豹麟'的珍兽，比猎犬大上少许，非常难得，我以高价搜罗，亦只得四张兽皮，今天一下子就用光了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "滕兄是否遇上什么开心的事？为何整个人脱胎换骨似的。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨天少龙在街上被人伏击一事，图爷已派人查过，应是渭南武士行馆的人，因为刚巧他们有两名武士昨天死了，秘密举行葬礼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "相国想请少龙暂时忍下这口气，因为相国有个更好的计划，可把阳泉君和邱日升一举除掉，所以不欲在此刻打草惊蛇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们高兴便来对付我们，迟早有人会给他们害了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "肖先生请相国放心，我们知道该怎么办的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "滕兄！好好享受这几天珍贵的光阴啊！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你也来调侃我！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天我请少龙来，是得到大王同意，好让我母子表示感激之意。现在朱姬再无所求，只望好好栽培政儿，使他将来能当个胜任的君主。",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还好这孩子并没有令我失望！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "姬后的心事，少龙明白。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知道你最明白我，见到你，不但像见到朋友，还像见到亲人，一点不须瞒你。你若有什么难题，不要怕向我说出来，有些情况由我向大王陈说，会比由相国禀告更为方便些。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiao_pan",
      "text": "政儿！琴太傅来了，快去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家又没有在你面前摆王后架子，为何话都不说多半句，忽然变成哑巴呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "守点君臣之礼，对姬后和我都是有利无害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我和你间很多话均不须说出来，不过人家真的很感激你。唉！早知道趁在邯郸的时候，把身体给你就好哩！至少可留下一段美丽的回忆。现在为做个好王后和好母后，所有私情都要放到一旁，希望少龙能体谅人家的心境。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看你！又变哑巴哩！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我可以说什么呢？应表示高兴还是不高兴？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看你还是高兴居多，那就不怕给朱姬牵累了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今趟少龙到邯郸，可否给我杀两个人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "说吧！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "第一个是赵穆的另一条走狗乐乘，但不要问我原因，我连想也不愿想起来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我定给你办到！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但太危险就不必，最紧要是你能无恙归来，没有了你，朱姬会感到失去一个好知己。由第一眼看到你开始，我便感到就算你不是我的情人，亦会是知心好友。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你当我在骗你吗？皇天在上，若我朱姬有一字虚言，教我不得善终！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "低声一点，给人听到就糟透了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没胆鬼！信了吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "还有一个人是谁呢？郭开吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "当然不是他，否则姬后那天早逼我杀了他哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算你还懂动脑筋，当然不是郭开，在那些可恶的人中，他对我算是很好的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "不要卖关子，快说吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是否无论我说出任何人，你都会照人家指示把他宰掉？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "还说我是你的知己，为何姬后总像要看我为难尴尬的样子？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好了！人家不再为难你了，另一个人就是……就是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "是否要我求你才肯说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当日大王和吕相逃离邯郸，赵穆知悉后，派乐乘率领大批人凶神恶煞般冲入家来，实时把所有男仆处死，女的给他们集体淫辱，那狰狞可怖的情景，到现在仍历历在目，就算白天不想，梦里仍会重历那凄惨不堪的景况，下令的人正是乐乘，你说他该杀吗？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "翌日我和假儿子给带到赵穆处软禁起来，那几天是我一生人最恶心的日子，当时我曾立下毒誓，假设将来有能力活着逃出生天，必报此辱。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "你仍未说那第二人是谁哩！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是赵雅！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么什么？下不了手吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "她究竟做过什么事？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家是骗你的，只是恨你对人家那毫不动心的可恶样儿，才找赵雅来吓唬你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "但除这部分外，其他的话都是千真万确。若情况许可，给人家把乐乘的首级带回来！算朱姬求你吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小心点啊！若换过是别人，我会说担保他荣华富贵。但我却知道你视功名如粪土，所以只能对你说声感激。若你有任何要求，只要说出来，朱姬定尽心尽力为你办妥。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 63,
